chart_description: This chart tracks the time that the kernel has been under memory pressure, and the number of processes that had to wait for memory to be reclaimed.

dimension_descriptions.some 10: This dimension indicates the duration of stall time when the memory pressure was at a low level.
dimension_descriptions.some 300: This dimension indicates the duration of stall time when the memory pressure was at a moderately high level.
dimension_descriptions.some 60: This dimension indicates the duration of stall time when the memory pressure was at a critical level.
